141
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:24,420
Room 207.

142
00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:26,780
Your food is here.

143
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:38,700
Pork joint.

144
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:39,660
Liver.

145
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:40,580
Chicken wings.

146
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:41,740
Bamboo shoots.

147
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:50,660
Ai yah.

148
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:54,300
Couldn't you come later?

149
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:57,260
Why must you
serve the dishes now?

